  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Casa Berno is set in an elevated mountain position overlooking the vast shores of Lake Maggiore. Set amongst a subtropical park you can explore the beautiful nature directly on your doorstep. The hotel shuttle is 8 minutes to <a data-udi="umb://document/f050bec61e8848ca96657eb5d251114a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f050bec61e8848ca96657eb5d251114a}" title="Ascona">Ascona</a> centre for easy access to excursion starting points.</p>
<p>Relaxation spots dotted around the hotel are designed to make the most of this enviable lakeside position. Visit the neatly furnished bar, comfortable lounge and the panoramic roof top sun terrace. Take a dip in the refreshing outdoor pool with a large lounging area and extended lake and mountain views. Head chef Romeo Corona serves regional culinary delights on the panoramic terrace and in the restaurant.</p>
<p>The gourmet food here is prepared using the finest local ingredients. There are weekly themed buffets and an outdoor barbecue. Ticino wines have been carefully selected for you to enjoy.</p>
<p>All bedrooms are bright and airy with neat furnishings and balcony for taking in your idyllic surroundings.</p>]]></description>
