  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Floor 1</strong></p>
<p>20m² 'Classic' twin rooms sleep 2-3 and have bath with showerhead (Garden view and only partial lake view from the balcony) </p>
<p><strong>Floors 2 &amp; 3</strong></p>
<p>20m² 'Panorama' rooms sleep 2-3 and have bath with showerhead </p>
<p>15m² 'Single panorama' rooms have bath with showerhead </p>
<p><strong>Floors 4 &amp; 5</strong></p>
<p>20m² 'Modern superior' rooms sleep 2 and have shower </p>
<p>35m² 'Panorama Junior Suites' sleep 2-4 and have double sofa bed and seperate sitting area </p>
<p>All the rooms are south-facing with balcony and lake views, and have bath or shower, TV, safe minibar and hairdryer.</p>
<p>Balconies have seating for you to relax and enjoy the views</p>]]></roomsDescription>
